<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Doctor Appointment App</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #4095c4, #ffffff); 
      color: #333;
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    .header .title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5em;
      text-align: center;
      flex: 1;
      margin-left: 200px; /* Margin to move title slightly right */
    }

    .header .nav-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0px; /* Reduced gap between buttons */
    }

    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      font-size: 1em;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #fff;
      background-color: #007BFF;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #3b34bc;
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .section {
      margin: 40px 0;
    }

    .section h2 {
      font-size: 2em;
      color: #007BFF;
    }

    .section p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      color: #555;
    }

    .hero-image {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 600px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .hero1 {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 500px;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .footer {
      background-color: #007BFF;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .footer p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1em;
    }

    .why-choose-us {
      text-align: center;
    }

    .why-choose-us p {
      font-size: 1.2em;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }

    .ad {
      width: 100%;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: white;
      font-size: larger;
    }

    .tile {
      color: white;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header class="header">
    <h1 class="title">BRIGHT HORIZON HEALTH</h1>
    <div class="nav-buttons">
      <a href="/register" class="button">Register</a>
      <a href="/login" class="button">Login</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <section class="section">
      <h2>Welcome to the Doctor Appointment App</h2>
      <p>Manage your medical appointments with ease. Our app helps you book, track, and view your appointments all in one place. Whether you need a routine check-up or a specialized consultation, we have you covered.</p>
      <a href="/book" class="button">Book an Appointment</a>
      <a href="/appointments" class="button">View Appointments</a>
    </section>

    <section class="section why-choose-us">
      <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
      <img src="/images/Daco_4739384.png" alt="text" class="hero"><br>
      <p>Our app offers a seamless experience for managing your health appointments. Hereâ€™s why you should choose us:</p>
      <p>Easy online booking and rescheduling</p>
      <p>View and manage your appointment history</p>
      <p>Receive reminders and notifications</p>
      <p>Access a wide range of medical specialists</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <img src="/images/appointments.jpg" alt="app" class="hero1"><br><br>
      <p>Getting started with our app is simple:</p>
      <p>Sign up or log in to your account.</p>
      <p>Choose your preferred doctor and available time slot.</p>
      <p>Confirm your appointment and receive a confirmation.</p>
      <p>Manage and view your appointments anytime.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <img src="/images/Doctor.jpg" alt="Doctor" class="hero-image">
    </section>
  </div>

  <footer class="footer">
    <a href="https://github.com/Rupali053" alt="github" class="ad">Follow Us</a><br>
    <a href="https://wecarehealthcenter.org/" alt="github1" class="ad">Follow Us For More Doctors</a><br>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Doctor Appointment App. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
